#### The mangle table
# This table allows us to modify packet headers
# Packets enter this table first
#
*mangle

:PREROUTING ACCEPT [0:0]
:INPUT ACCEPT [0:0]
:FORWARD ACCEPT [0:0]
:OUTPUT ACCEPT [0:0]
:POSTROUTING ACCEPT [0:0]

